From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kernel-builder <builder@github.com>
Date: Fri, 6 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: add forward declaration for enum mmu_notifier_event

Fix Clang compilation error on kernel 4.19 with KVM enabled:
  variable has incomplete type 'enum mmu_notifier_event'

Signed-off-by: kernel-builder <builder@github.com>
---
 include/linux/mmu_notifier.h | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/include/linux/mmu_notifier.h b/include/linux/mmu_notifier.h
index 1b61c2a90..f8e1c3c45 100644
--- a/include/linux/mmu_notifier.h
+++ b/include/linux/mmu_notifier.h
@@ -343,6 +343,8 @@ static inline int mmu_notifier_clear_flush_young(struct mm_struct *mm)
 	return 0;
 }
 
+enum mmu_notifier_event;
+
 static inline void mmu_notifier_change_pte(struct mm_struct *mm,
 		unsigned long address, pte_t pte)
 {
